386
00:15:45,084 --> 00:15:46,244
too many times.

387
00:15:47,084 --> 00:15:48,524
I must see your parents this time.

388
00:15:48,884 --> 00:15:49,524
Mr. Xie,

389
00:15:49,844 --> 00:15:51,124
I can do everything you say.

390
00:15:51,124 --> 00:15:52,524
