606
00:24:21,564 --> 00:24:22,324
Eat up.

607
00:24:23,324 --> 00:24:24,564
Here, eat more.

608
00:24:24,684 --> 00:24:25,404
Thanks, Aunt.

609
00:24:25,884 --> 00:24:26,844
Here, eat the dumplings.

610
00:24:27,324 --> 00:24:28,524
