00:25:09,844 --> 00:25:10,924
to see you in person.

617
00:25:11,764 --> 00:25:12,764
Sorry.

618
00:25:13,244 --> 00:25:14,244
I was too busy.

619
00:25:15,524 --> 00:25:16,084
Yes.

620
00:25:17,084 --> 00:25:17,964
Even so,

621
00:25:17,964 --> 00:25:19,724
