What's going on?

643
00:26:01,484 --> 00:26:02,364
Just trust my mom.

644
00:26:02,964 --> 00:26:04,284
I'm sure she has a mind of her own.

645
00:26:04,364 --> 00:26:05,724
What do you mean?

646
